{"tid":2016861,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"明居正: 習近平會攞香港做籌碼。","createTime":"2020-05-14T17:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T18:09:02.000Z","uid":62011,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"656ce44be9f2282d0766711e23c7189fee3099ef","tid":2016861,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=maPZlHIRcfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmaPZlHIRcfo&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7lUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=65ac5df3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=maPZlHIRcfo</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單講:<br />\n中國依家內外交困，得返兩條路走，一就係研發疫苗(個人意見: 佢偷美國資料就證明佢無能力研發解藥)；第二，攞香港做籌碼，威脅鎮壓香港，影響其他國家係香港利益，然後提出唔好向中共索償。所以港共先後捉拿泛民，今日一次過控訴32個人暴動罪。"},{"pid":"385ee140e6d2e48df2d5a404fafac645af1b6c53","tid":2016861,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"719029844dfdcdfc1d2c04e0d94e920bdef5075f","tid":2016861,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"中国的確係死淨香港呢張牌<br />\n但對手唔係英國<br />\n<br />\n美國點解要無條件幫香港？"},{"pid":"edddf4e055178b1dcd935a7875955b11e2ed23f3","tid":2016861,"uid":223741,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:13:49.000Z","msg":"明居正估香港既事<br />\n成日都估錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63c9c6f77f08bb3b62db2fcdc098dc38c2c48cc","tid":2016861,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:14:15.000Z","msg":"如果真係行第二條路<br />\n香港之後會好血腥<br />\n到真正光復之前一定死好多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c2f0b9009df058ac7d1a7f93376a902816fcf4","tid":2016861,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"咁真係玩完<br />\n用攬炒要脅人咁撚賤都有<br />\n佢嗰種攬炒炒完冇得重生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cl